# Smart Parking Management System

## Abstract

The Smart Parking System is a web-based application developed using Java Servlets, JSP, MySQL, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Apache Tomcat. The system aims to simplify parking management by allowing users to search for available parking spaces, make bookings, and calculate parking charges automatically. The application provides an efficient solution for reducing the time spent searching for parking spots and improves overall parking lot utilization. The project was developed as part of a Java and Database Management System course.

---

# 1. Introduction

With the increasing number of vehicles in urban areas, finding available parking spaces has become a significant challenge. Traditional parking systems often result in traffic congestion, wasted fuel, and frustration for drivers. The Smart Parking System addresses these issues by providing an online platform where users can view parking availability, reserve parking spots, and manage bookings efficiently.

The system automates parking slot management and provides real-time information regarding parking availability, making the parking process more convenient and user-friendly.

