# 5. Functional Modules

## 5.1 User Registration and Login

Users can create an account and securely log in to access parking services.

### Features:

* User Registration
* User Authentication
* Session Management

---

## 5.2 Parking Lot Browsing

Users can browse available parking locations and view parking slot availability.

### Features:

* Search Parking Areas
* View Available Slots
* Parking Lot Details

---

## 5.3 Current Booking

Users can book currently available parking slots instantly.

### Features:

* Real-Time Slot Availability
* Immediate Reservation
* Booking Confirmation

---

## 5.4 Future Booking

The system supports advance reservations for specific dates and times.

### Features:

* Schedule Parking
* Time-Based Reservation
* Advance Planning

---

## 5.5 Fare Calculation

Parking charges are automatically calculated based on the duration of parking and predefined rates.

### Features:

* Automated Billing
* Duration-Based Pricing
* Booking Summary

The repository specifically mentions support for current booking, future booking, and automatic fare calculation.

